        <mxCell id="note" value="Skewed wavefront (reference mini-TPU pattern scaled to N=4): line i streams during t ∈ [i+1, i+4]; PE[i][c] combines A element k with W step k at t = i+c+1+k. RUN completes at t = 10. After power-up, one throwaway RUN flushes random values from the no-reset pipeline registers. K = 4 divides the NVFP4 16-element block exactly (4 tiles per block)." style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=11;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;" vertex="1" parent="1">
